data.description: Breathtaking Hill Country Hilltop Israel Pena Masterpiece with Exquisite Views, nestled in the serene landscape of rolling hills and panoramic views that stretch as far as the eye can see! The house itself is a craftsman style with rich hardwood cabinetry and trim, giant windows galore, spacious gourmet kitchen a new smart double oven, plus gas cooktop. Pristine master retreat has views of the sunrise from bed! New water heater, three car garage, mud room, study (or library.)Upstairs 4th bedroom w/half bath could be a game room. Neighborhood river park/playground with fishing pier and tennis, and sport court. Newly painted exterior with 25 year warranty. John Deer riding lawnmower included!
